Run the demo
* Update the file: https://github.com/jfdenise/wildfly-core/blob/cli-ai/cli/src/main/java/org/jboss/as/cli/handlers/chatbot/ChatBotControlFlow.java#L61
with your OPEN AI API KEY.
* Build wildfly-core
* cd cli
* Start the CLI fat jar (no JBoss Modules yet): java -jar target/wildfly-cli-24.0.0.Beta3-SNAPSHOT-client.jar
* To go to ChatBot mode type: chat
* Once in chat mode, type the Question. For example: How to configure Logging with CLI?
* To leave the ChatBot mode type: bye

